          "briefTitle": "A Single Arm, Phase Ib/II Trial of Single Agent Pacritinib in Patients With 1q21.3 Amplified Solid Tumors Enriching for Interleukin-1 Receptor-associated Kinase 1 Pathway Activation (PAIR)",
          "officialTitle": "A Single Arm, Phase Ib/II Trial of Single Agent Pacritinib in Patients With 1q21.3 Amplified Solid Tumors Enriching for Interleukin-1 Receptor-associated Kinase 1 (IRAK1) Pathway Activation (PAIR)"
        },
