          "officialTitle": "The Safety, Tolerability and Biodistribution of a Single Intravenous Administration of Two Zirconium-89 Labelled Vartumabs (F8scFV or C9scFv) in Patients With Solid Tumors - a Phase 0, Open Label, PET/CT Molecular Imaging Basket Trial",
